                        <h1 class="text-primary mb-4">Careers</h1>
                        <p class="mb-4">We are revolutionising insurance by providing consumers with a better, easier and up to 80% cheaper solution. We call this <strong>Social Insurance</strong>. Starting with mobile phones, so-sureâ€™s ambition is to expand rapidly across consumer lines and geographies over the next few years. If you're keen to help us out, please do send us a note to <a href="mailto:hello@spam.so-sure.net" class="mailto append-email">jobs</a>.</p>
                        <div class="mb-4"><script data-startup="so-sure" src="https://angel.co/javascripts/embed_jobs.js" id="angellist_embed" async></script></div>
